name: Upper Tree of Life 08
description: Part 8 of a 28 minute video (each part in a series of 11), these parts can be joined together to make the full 28 minute video (1440p,60fps). Upper Tree of Life is a Virtual Reality interpretation of an acrylic painting study on the Kabbalah Tree of Life. Called the Upper Tree of Life, this is the divine version of the Kabbalah Tree. Video capture of a VR painting using Tilt Brush and Open Brush, original music by Barry Chabala (barrychabala.bandcamp.com/   IG: @barry.chabala.roeba.recordings   Twitter: @BarryChabala). The remaining parts of the video will be released in the upcoming days/weeks. Kabbalah, VR, VR Painting, OpenBrush, Original Music, Sacred Geometry, Visual, Digital
